.DT
set_night_long
Discworld outside help
set_night_long

Name
.SI 5
set_night_long - The description for those nights.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_night_long(string str);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This sets the night long.  This is different to the dark long cause night
and dark don't nessarialy follow.  If this is set the dark long is never
used.  With this set it also gives an inventory list, unlike with the
dark long.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
set_dark_long, query_night_long
.EP
